title: Amy’s Garlic Feet Experiment + Food Feud: Flamin’ Hot Cheetos vs. Cool Ranch Doritos + Maddie And Tae Emotional During Quarantine
itunes:title: Amy’s Garlic Feet Experiment + Food Feud: Flamin’ Hot Cheetos vs. Cool Ranch Doritos + Maddie And Tae Emotional During Quarantine
description:
Amy's fun fact says if you put your foot into a bag of garlic, you’ll be able to taste the garlic. We put it to the test! In today's 'Food Feud', we put Flamin’ Hot Cheetos up against Cool Ranch Doritos. Plus, Maddie and Tae stop by to talk about their new song that’s climbing the charts, being emotional during quarantine and being mask shamed by some teenagers!
